query: SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget, MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes, MIN(n.name) AS writer, MIN(t.title) AS complete_gore_movie FROM complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, cast_info AS ci, info_type AS it1, info_type AS it2, keyword AS k, movie_info AS mi, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, title AS t WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND t.title not like '%island%' AND t.title not like '%key%' AND t.title not like '%mystery%' AND t.production_year > 2003 AND it1.info not in ('book','languages','printed media reviews','death date','LD sharpness') AND cct2.kind in ('crew','complete+verified') AND k.keyword not like '%spy%' AND k.keyword not like '%evil%' AND it2.info not in ('LD aspect ratio','other works','LD spaciality','LD digital sound','LD category','votes','LD disc size','novel','LD frequency response','birth notes','plot','color info','budget','death date','spouse','LD picture format','LD language') AND mi.info not in ('Hindi','Tagalog','Yiddish','Vietnamese','Korean','Ukrainian')
